dency of porosity. 0: constant, else changing with depth (i.e. distanc
e)\n" }{TEXT 26 5 "vpor0" }{TEXT 320 50 ": porosity value (either cons
tant or else at x=0)\n" }{TEXT 26 6 "viarea" }{TEXT 320 96 ": depth de
pendency of cross section area. 0: constant, else changing with depth \+
