 area (either constant or else at x=0, L^2)\n" }{TEXT 320 99 "- user s
pecified profiles of por(x) or area(x) must be defined in the fortran \+
subroutine porarea.f." }}}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 13 "vi
